            <div class="title">
                Budget Proposals And Economic Survey
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1950-04-19/debates/066f8229-90c6-4ea0-a30a-cd135aaef51c/FinanceMoney" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
