<p class=""><em>indicated assent.</em></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bcd68d94-fcf8-4fb7-92cd-bd0478cbf6c5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
