<p class="">Perhaps I can relieve the feelings of the hon. Member for Chesterfield (Mr. Benson). I thought I made it clear that we did not wish to see avoidance of Surtax of this sort.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
