<p class="">It is not the Chairman of the Committee who makes the report; it is the Committee, upon which the Government have, of course, a substantial majority.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-aff8e04d-7c36-4304-88ee-32e079a2a907" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
