<p class="">Will not the hon. Gentleman find the explanation of the discrepancy in the appendices at the end of this document—" National Income and Expenditure of the United Kingdom, 1946 to 1949"?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d463dcde-d6d6-4f59-9d58-3facab69d6e6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
